{
  "text": "Although there have been studies that evaluated the overall health status of working children and adolescents, few studies have assessed the oral/dental health and OHRQoL of adolescent workers [CITATION_1] . Therefore, the results of the present study provide valuable information about a relatively neglected population.",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "7057456"
